trans-unit.source: Specifies which parts are included in a message.
trans-unit.target: Angir hvilke deler er inkludert i en melding.

trans-unit.source: This class contains the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.MessagePartSpecification> instances of different messages, each distinguished by the message Action.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen inneholder den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.MessagePartSpecification>forekomster av ulike meldinger hver identifiseres med meldingen handling.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.MessagePartSpecification>

trans-unit.source: Gets a message part specification that contains the channel parts.
trans-unit.target: Henter en spesifikasjonen for meldingsdelen som inneholder delene kanal.

trans-unit.source: The channel parts denote the message parts that are common to all the messages.
trans-unit.target: Kanal delene angir deler av meldinger som er felles for alle meldinger.

trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Security.MessagePartSpecification"> </xref> som inneholder delene kanal.

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether the specification is read-only.
trans-unit.target: Angir om spesifikasjonen er skrivebeskyttet.

trans-unit.source: You can use <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.ScopedMessagePartSpecification.MakeReadOnly%2A> to set this property to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.ScopedMessagePartSpecification.MakeReadOnly%2A>å angi denne egenskapen `true`.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.ScopedMessagePartSpecification.MakeReadOnly%2A>

trans-unit.source: Checks whether there are parts that match a given action key.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollerer om det deler som samsvarer med en gitt handlingen nøkkel.

trans-unit.source: If the given action is not present in the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.ScopedMessagePartSpecification>, then the message parts configured for the Wildcard action ("*") are returned.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den angitte handlingen ikke finnes i den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.ScopedMessagePartSpecification>, og deretter meldingsdeler som er konfigurert for handlingen jokertegn ("*") returneres.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.ScopedMessagePartSpecification>

trans-unit.source: The action key.
trans-unit.target: Nøkkelen for handlingen.

trans-unit.source: When this method returns, contains a <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Security.MessagePartSpecification"></xref> that contains the parts found.
